text: Édouard Leguery (8 August 1934 - 16 February 1986) was a French rower. He competed at the 1956 Summer Olympics in Melbourne with the men's eight where they were eliminated in the round one heat. ==References== == External links == * Category:1934 births Category:1986 deaths Category:French male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of France Category:Rowers at the 1956 Summer Olympics Category:European Rowing Championships medalists
